review_data: Reviewed in the United States on March 12, 2021
name: Dozo
title: Awesome Greek Yogurt
review: They've made it hard to find, sometimes, by changing the name from Wallaby to Aussie Greek and then back to Wallaby, plus often stores only carry the lowfat or nonfat versions, or the Vanilla one, but this is by far the best yogurt, thick and rich with a touch of sweetness.If I'm looking for very tart, I go with Fage but for a tasty treat, I love this, and to get very decadent drizzled with a tiny bit of maple syrup or local honey, it's amazing.Their sour cream is also lovely, but very hard to find.
